name: Genesis Cyberhorse Collection - Bane
description: Bane is part of a strikeforce that is deployed by a alien race set on conquering the galaxy. His job is to get all sea creatures to submit to their rule and he's damn good at it. He's intelligent, ferocious, and the tactical leader of his team. Ocular laser beams, spiked shell able to generate volcanic matter for self-defense. Equipped with state of the art radar, lidar, and processes probability data for each encounter that is used to his advantage when facing his enemies.#Fear4Hen
